h4. Actor:
Administrator, Remittance User.

h4. Description: 
Name of use case represent its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Project Track|guide:_ShowProjectTrackPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Settings" sub menu from left menu.
* Click *Purchase Instrument Mapping* link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Purchase Instrument Mapping"|guide:ShowRmsPurchaseInstrumentMappingActionService].
* Populate "Bank Wise District" List in drop-down.

h4. Pre-condition: 
* User must have "Reload District dropdown independently" privilege.

h4. Process: 
* Get "Bank Wise District" list from server. [Show Landing Page of "District"|guide:ShowDistrictActionService]

h4. Post-condition: 

* *Success:*
** Populate all "Bank Wise District" list in drop down.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

